---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Us - Get Global Yields"
  description="Learn about the dedicated team behind Get Global Yields."
>
  <div class="bg-primary-900 py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 max-w-4xl">
      <article class="prose prose-invert prose-lg prose-a:text-accent-500 hover:prose-a:text-accent-400 max-w-none">
        <h1>About Get Global Yields</h1>
        <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-300">
          Welcome to Get Global Yields. We are a dedicated team of finance enthusiasts, researchers, and writers committed to uncovering the best financial products and investment opportunities worldwide.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-slate-100">Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          In an increasingly complex global financial landscape, finding reliable information can be daunting. Our mission is to demystify high-yield accounts, investment platforms, and personal finance strategies. We aim to provide clear, actionable insights that empower our readers to maximize their returns and achieve greater financial independence.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-slate-100">What We Do</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>In-Depth Reviews:</strong> We rigorously analyze financial products, breaking down the pros, cons, and hidden fees so you know exactly what you're signing up for.</li>
          <li><strong>Comparative Analysis:</strong> Our side-by-side comparisons help you weigh your options effectively before making a commitment.</li>
          <li><strong>Educational Guides:</strong> Whether you're a seasoned investor or just starting, our step-by-step guides offer valuable strategies to enhance your portfolio.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-slate-100">Why Trust Us?</h2>
        <p>
          Integrity and transparency are at the core of what we do. While we may earn affiliate commissions on some products we recommend, our reviews are always independent and unbiased. We prioritize your financial well-being above all else.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
